  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Q: What kind of game is this?</strong><br><strong>A:</strong> It’s a 3D game where you bounce on a Pogo Stick and try to climb a massive tower full of tricky obstacles. Mess up a jump, and you’re flying back down to the bottom. Yeah, it’s brutal, but that’s what makes it so addictive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/f006ea31414fba3ef7e24b68a405b60b.avif?t=1737980817\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras_big/f006ea31414fba3ef7e24b68a405b60b.avif?t=1737980817 width=800 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/363afc8cc576fee7d086fd3c64bf5127.poster.avif?t=1737980817\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/363afc8cc576fee7d086fd3c64bf5127.webm?t=1737980817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/363afc8cc576fee7d086fd3c64bf5127.mp4?t=1737980817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game throws all kinds of wild stuff at you—springy platforms, moving traps, and unpredictable challenges. Each section is different, keeping you on edge and making every jump feel like a mini-adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/3518f31b0a71bde159b75ca0f6df219a.poster.avif?t=1737980817\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/3518f31b0a71bde159b75ca0f6df219a.webm?t=1737980817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/3518f31b0a71bde159b75ca0f6df219a.mp4?t=1737980817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then there are moments where it’s just you, your Pogo Stick, and the cliffs. Use the environment to pull off tricks, find shortcuts, or blaze your own trail to the top. The freedom to experiment makes every climb feel personal and rewarding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you’ve got the skill and patience to reach the top?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Q: What kind of game is this?</strong><br><strong>A:</strong> It’s a 3D game where you bounce on a Pogo Stick and try to climb a massive tower full of tricky obstacles. Mess up a jump, and you’re flying back down to the bottom. Yeah, it’s brutal, but that’s what makes it so addictive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/f006ea31414fba3ef7e24b68a405b60b.avif?t=1737980817\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras_big/f006ea31414fba3ef7e24b68a405b60b.avif?t=1737980817 width=800 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/363afc8cc576fee7d086fd3c64bf5127.poster.avif?t=1737980817\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/363afc8cc576fee7d086fd3c64bf5127.webm?t=1737980817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/363afc8cc576fee7d086fd3c64bf5127.mp4?t=1737980817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game throws all kinds of wild stuff at you—springy platforms, moving traps, and unpredictable challenges. Each section is different, keeping you on edge and making every jump feel like a mini-adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/3518f31b0a71bde159b75ca0f6df219a.poster.avif?t=1737980817\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/3518f31b0a71bde159b75ca0f6df219a.webm?t=1737980817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409720/extras/3518f31b0a71bde159b75ca0f6df219a.mp4?t=1737980817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then there are moments where it’s just you, your Pogo Stick, and the cliffs. Use the environment to pull off tricks, find shortcuts, or blaze your own trail to the top. The freedom to experiment makes every climb feel personal and rewarding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you’ve got the skill and patience to reach the top?</p>",
